title: Nepali Play- Jodiyos Bhattkieka Manharu
desc: a Nepali play titled ?Jodiyos Bhatkiyeka Manharu? is going to be staged on Off-Broadway Theatre (777 Theatre-777 8th Ave Between 47th & 48th Sts) in Manhattan of NewYork City known as the capital of the performing arts.     The one-hour play Written by Ashesh Malla and Directed by Hari Bahadur Thapa with the cast of New York City Nepali theatre actors.     Venue: 777 Theatre-777th 8th Ave   Date: December 13
